# ARC Wellness project context

This workspace contains the **ARC Wellness** marketing website (homepage and related routes).

## Project type

- **Next.js** (App Router) + **React**
- **Tailwind CSS** v4 for styling
- **Framer Motion** for component / hero motion
- **GSAP** (+ ScrollTrigger where used) for scroll-driven animation
- Optional **next/image** for optimized imagery

## Brand & tone

- Premium **medical aesthetics + wellness + longevity** positioning
- Visual language: **muted teal** (`~#76B3A8`), **cream / off-white** backgrounds, **charcoal** typography
- **Serif** for headlines, **clean sans** for UI and body (see theme in `src/app/layout.tsx` and `globals.css`)
- Calm, elevated, intentional—not generic spa templates or loud clinical stock UI

## Primary homepage sections (baseline)

- Hero with scroll-driven media expand (when enabled)
- Who we are
- Whole-body care / services
- Patient journey (“Your path”)
- Invest / lifestyle CTA band
- Footer with contact and links

When suggesting or implementing changes, preserve this positioning and quality bar. Do not strip brand colors or swap to unrelated palettes unless explicitly requested.
